title: I Can Cook " Cake Baking"
description: A Children's Simple Bake Book with simple step by step instructions. A beginners Baking book ideal for your children who will instantly learn to make these simple cake recipes with adult guidance and supervision. In NO time your children will be making these delicious fun Cakes and more just like my grand daughter "Imsi" did. Enjoy your time baking and cooking with kids.
author: Marika Germanis
